OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,FITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,7,Freports on the final day of the King
OL,8,Fand Queen's state visit to the United
OL,9,FStates
OL,11,FThe King and Queen have bid farewell
OL,12,Fto US President Donald Trump and First
OL,13,FLady Melania Trump, as their four-day
OL,14,Ftrip celebrating America's 250th
OL,15,Fanniversary draws to a close.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
