OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,FAfter leaving the White House, Charles
OL,7,Fand Camilla visited Arlington National
OL,8,FCemetery in Virginia on Thursday and
OL,9,Flaid a wreath at the Tomb of the
OL,10,FUnknown Soldier to honour the fallen
OL,11,Fand mark the UK-US military
OL,12,Fpartnership.
OL,14,FThis comes after the Queen described
OL,15,Fher US state visit with the King as
OL,16,F"wonderful" in a brief interview with
OL,17,FNBC's Today breakfast show, which was
OL,18,Faired on Thursday.
