OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,FSpeaking during the royal couple's
OL,7,Fvisit to New York, Camilla said: "It's
OL,8,Fbeen a whistlestop. It's been really
OL,9,Fgood fun, but we have moved quite
OL,10,Ffast."
OL,12,FShe added: "It's been wonderful and
OL,13,Feverybody's been very kind and
OL,14,Fwelcoming.
OL,16,F"It's always a pleasure to be here.
OL,18,F"Always lovely to be back in New York."
