OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,FThe brief chat took place during the
OL,7,FQueen's visit to the New York Public
OL,8,FLibrary, where she highlighted her
OL,9,Fbook club, The Queen's Reading Room,
OL,10,Fand celebrated literature with guests,
OL,11,Fincluding Sex and the City star Sarah
OL,12,FJessica Parker.
OL,14,FCamilla mentioned how her love of
OL,15,Freading stemmed from her father, she
OL,16,Fsaid: "Oh, but he was wonderful.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
