OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,F"He used to sit at the end of our beds
OL,7,Fevery night and read us these
OL,8,Fincredibly exciting stories, some of
OL,9,Fthem quite frightening, pillows over
OL,10,Four head, but he just gave us this
OL,11,Fincredible interest.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe royal couple ended their busy day
OL,19,Fin New York at an event celebrating
OL,20,Fthe King's Trust work and showcasing
OL,21,Fthe UK's cultural impact on New York.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
