OL,3,CKing and Queen bid farewell to Trump
OL,4,Cas US state visit comes to a close
OL,6,FSuperstar singer Lionel Richie, on the
OL,7,Ftrust's global ambassador, praised the
OL,8,FKing's speech to the US Congress,
OL,9,Fdescribing Charles as a wise friend
OL,10,F"giving advice as to what we should be
OL,11,Fdoing".
OL,13,FThe gathering featured a host of
OL,14,Fcelebrities who included Italian
OL,15,Ffashion designer Donatella Versace,
OL,16,Ffashion guru Anna Wintour, British
OL,17,Fcreative Stella McCartney and model
OL,18,FIman.
